Class AlignofExpression

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Intrinsic, Printable, Traversable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Expression>
public class AlignofExpression
extends Expression
implements Intrinsic

AlignofExpression represents the non-standard __alignof__ operation. It is implemented as an expression just for convenience.
